feat: implement InterfaceHive-inspired design system with dark/light themes

Complete frontend redesign with modern, clean aesthetic featuring bold typography, geometric branding, and sophisticated color palette:

- **Design System**:
  - Created comprehensive CSS variable system for dark/light themes
  - Dark theme: Deep navy (#0a0f1e) with orange/amber accents (#f59e0b)
  - Light theme: Cream/beige background (#fefce8) with matching accents
  - Custom typography scale using Inter and Space Grotesk fonts
  - Reusable component classes (buttons, cards, inputs, badges)
  - Smooth animations (fade-in, slide-up, scale-in, glow-pulse)
  - Custom scrollbar styling and focus ring patterns

- **New Components**:
  - HexagonLogo: Geometric double-hexagon SVG with configurable size and glow effect
  - ThemeToggle: Sun/Moon icon toggle with persistent localStorage
  - ThemeContext: Global theme state management with CSS custom properties

- **Redesigned Pages & Components**:
  - LoginPage/RegisterPage: Centered layouts with decorative gradient orbs and icon-enhanced inputs
  - DashboardLayout: Dark sidebar with orange active states and glow effects
  - ProjectsPage: Grid layout with hover effects and gradient project cards
  - KanbanBoard: Clean columns with color-coded headers and smooth drag-and-drop
  - TaskCard: Role badges, priority indicators, and orange accent interactions

- **Visual Features**:
  - Bold headings (48-72px) with orange highlighted keywords
  - Staggered entrance animations (0.1s increments)
  - Hover glow effects on interactive elements
  - Seamless theme switching with 0.3s transitions
  - High contrast text ratios (WCAG AA+)
  - Responsive design with mobile-friendly sidebar

- **Technical Updates**:
  - Downgraded Tailwind CSS from v4 to v3.4.1 for stability
  - Updated PostCSS configuration for compatibility
  - Converted CSS variables to regular properties for Tailwind v3
  - Created DESIGN_SYSTEM.md documentation

- **Configuration**:
  - Added postcss.config.js with proper Tailwind v3 setup
  - Updated package.json with tailwindcss@^3.4.1 dependency
  - Configured proper font imports (Inter, Space Grotesk)

This redesign delivers a production-ready, professional interface with distinctive orange accents, geometric hexagonal branding, and seamless dark/light mode functionality.
